      "description": "Hey there! It\u2019s honestly a bit bittersweet to be posting this, but it\u2019s time for this beauty to find a new home. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car\u2014it\u2019s been my pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and treated to hand-washes only. You\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a speck of dust on her, let alone a scratch; she truly looks and smells like she just rolled off the showroom floor. It drives like an absolute dream, smooth and responsive, just like the day I bought it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and maintained to the highest standard, you\u2019ve found it. Drop by, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and I\u2019ll show you why this car is so special!",
      "price": 48500.0,
