      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to exceed factory specifications. This S54 powerplant exhibits peak volumetric efficiency with a bulletproofed VANOS system and recent rod bearing prophylaxis. The chassis dynamics are razor-sharp, featuring reinforced subframe mounting points and a bespoke suspension geometry setup that eliminates turn-in understeer. Every gear change through the Getrag unit is crisp, delivering power to the rear via a perfectly shimmed M-Variable differential. This isn't just a driver; it's a precision instrument with zero parasitic loss or thermal soak issues. Turn-key and ready for the apex.",
      "price": 44500.0,
