      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine a machine that doesn't just transport you, but transcends time itself. This is not merely a car; it is a preserved whisper of automotive perfection, a silver-scaled dragon waiting to breathe life into the open road. Every curve of its bodywork catches the light like a polished diamond, and the interior welcomes you with the scent of heritage and the embrace of untouched craftsmanship. To drive it is to conduct a symphony of steel and soul, turning every mundane errand into a cinematic escape. This is your chance to own a masterpiece that feels as if it were driven straight out of a dream and into your driveway.",
